### Bất Động Sản API - HTTP Test File
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000

---

### ✅ HEALTH CHECKS

### 1. Root Endpoint
GET http://localhost:8000/

---

### 2. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

---

### 🌍 PROVINCES

### 1. Get All Provinces
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/provinces/

---

### 2. Get Districts by Province ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/provinces/01/districts

---

### 3. Get Districts by Province Name (Hà Nội)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/districts?province_name=Hà%20Nội

---

### 4. Get Average Price by Province
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/provinces/avg-price-per-m2?province_name=Hà%20Nội

---

### 4b. Get Average Price by Province with Type Filter
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/provinces/avg-price-per-m2?province_name=Hà%20Nội&type_id=nha-o

---

### 🏘️ DISTRICTS

### 5. Get Wards by District ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/wards/001

---

### 6. Get Wards by District Name (Quận Ba Đình)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/wards?district_name=Ba%20Đình

---

### 7. Get Average Price by District
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/districts/avg-price-per-m2?district_name=Ba%20Đình

---

### 7b. Get Average Price by District with Type Filter
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/districts/avg-price-per-m2?district_name=Quận%20Ba%20Đình&type_id=nha-o

---

### 🏠 WARDS

### 8. Get Average Price by Ward
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/wards/avg-price-per-m2?ward_name=Phường%20Phúc%20Xá

---

### 8b. Get Average Price by Ward with Type Filter
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/wards/avg-price-per-m2?ward_name=Phường%20Phúc%20Xá&type_id=nha-o

---

### 📊 ANALYTICS

### 9. Get Price Analysis by Address (Nominatim)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/price/by-address
Content-Type: application/json

< payload.json

###

### 10. Get Price Analysis by Address (with Mapbox Fallback)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/price/by-address
Content-Type: application/json

< payload.json

###

### 11. Get Projects by District
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/projects/district?district_name=Ba%20Đình

---

### 12. Get Projects by Ward
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/projects/ward?ward_name=phúc%20Xá

---

### 📈 PRICE BY DISTRICT NAME - NEW ENDPOINT

### 13. Get Monthly Average Price by District Name (12 months)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/price/by-district-name?district_name=Ba%20Đình

---

### 13b. Get Monthly Average Price by District with Type Filter
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/price/by-district-name?district_name=Quận%20Ba%20Đình&type_id=nha-o

---

### 13c. Get Monthly Average Price - Invalid District (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/price/by-district-name?district_name=Huyện_Không_Tồn_Tại

---

### 13d. Get Monthly Average Price - Another Valid District
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/price/by-district-name?district_name=Quận%201

---

### 📊 PRICE BY PROVINCE NAME - NEW ENDPOINT

### 14. Get Monthly Average Price by Province Name (12 months)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/price/by-province-name?province_name=Hà%20Nội

---

### 14b. Get Monthly Average Price by Province with Type Filter
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/price/by-province-name?province_name=Hà%20Nội&type_id=nha-o

---

### 14c. Get Monthly Average Price - Invalid Province (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/price/by-province-name?province_name=Tỉnh_Không_Tồn_Tại

---

### 14d. Get Monthly Average Price - Another Valid Province
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/price/by-province-name?province_name=Hồ%20Chí%20Minh

---

### 🏘️ LISTINGS (Danh sách nhà)

### 15. Get Listings by District Name
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/listings/by-district?district_name=Quận%201

---

### 15b. Get Listings by District with Type Filter
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/listings/by-district?district_name=Quận%20Ba%20Đình&type_id=nha-o

---

### 15c. Get Listings by District with Limit
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/listings/by-district?district_name=Quận%201&limit=50

---

### 16. Get Listings by Ward Name
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/listings/by-ward?ward_name=Phúc%20Xá

---

### 16b. Get Listings by Ward with Type Filter
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/listings/by-ward?ward_name=Phường%20Phúc%20Xá&type_id=nha-o

---

### 16c. Get Listings by Ward with Limit
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/listings/by-ward?ward_name=Phường%20Phúc%20Xá&limit=50

